ont-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>责任描述：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>1. Kafka收集BSBank中的流水数据和Flume的日志数据<br />2. Spark Streaming从kafka中获取数据，通过Spark进行一次一次粗过滤<br />3. Kettle获取粗过滤结果，链接机构表，生成报表数据抛送到前端<br />4. Echarts异步获取整理好的数据，定时器5s异步获取。<br /></span><span  lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:5;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>项目描述：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>815项目上线期间，ECC中心半实时的监控各网点的上线数据情况，通过Kafka从所以BSBank的服务器获取所有营业网店的流水数据，通过Flume获取日志数据，Spark Streaming作为队列信息的消费者模型，Spark从Kafka的节点中获取相关数据，进行计算， Kettle读取数据，将数据进行清洗过滤，生成动态报表，Ajax异步获取数据，展现在Echarts上。</span>  <span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes\'>  <td width=712 colspan=2 valign=top style=\'width:534.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:  normal\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:  Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;  mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;  mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>2014.07 - 2015.03  包商银行运营管控系统决策分析模块</span>  <span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt;background:#D9D9D9;mso-shading:white;mso-pattern:gray-15 auto\'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:1\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>软件环境：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>HDFS+Hbase+MapReduce +DB2+Sqoop+SPOON KETTLE+ECharts</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:4\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme