\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>责任描述：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>1. Kafka收集BSBank中的流水数据和Flume的日志数据<br />2. Spark Streaming从kafka中获取数据，通过Spark进行一次一次粗过滤<br />3. Kettle获取粗过滤结果，链接机构表，生成报表数据抛送到前端<br />4. Echarts异步获取整理好的数据，定时器5s异步获取。<br /></span><span  lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:5;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>项目描述：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>815项目上线期间，ECC中心半实时的监控各网点的上线数据情况，通过Kafka从所以BSBank的服务器获取所有营业网店的流水数据，通过Flume获取日志数据，Spark Streaming作为队列信息的消费者模型，Spark从Kafka的节点中获取相关数据，进行计算， Kettle读取数据，将数据进行清洗过滤，生成动态报表，Ajax异步获取数据，展现在Echarts上。</span>  <span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes\'>  <td width=712 colspan=2 valign=top style=\'width:534.1pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:  normal\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:  Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;  mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;  mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>2014.07 - 2015.03  包商银行运营管控系统决策分析模块</span>  <span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt;background:#D9D9D9;mso-shading:white;mso-pattern:gray-15 auto\'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:1\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>软件环境：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>HDFS+Hbase+MapReduce +DB2+Sqoop+SPOON KETTLE+ECharts</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:4\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>责任描述：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>1. 数据通过MR进行相应格式的转换和过滤<br />2. 将整理过的数据，进行Hive的多维度分析，按照员工、机构等不同维度进行统计<br />3. 把Hive分析结果导入到DB2中<br />4. 通过Kettle进行二次整理，重新写入数据库<br />5. 前端展示以Echarts开发，以简单的查询SQL，根据员工输入的查询条件，在DB2中取出相应的结果数据，生成数据报表和图表，并提供导出PDF等操作，月度生成整合的机构报表，提供给总行清算中心的分管领导进行决策。对于员工和行内的差错报表，会推送到人行，进行行间的考核。</span><span  lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr> <tr style=\'mso-yfti-irow:5;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\'>  <td width=111 valign=top style=\'width:83.4pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>项目描述：</span><span lang=EN-US  style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td>  <td width=601 valign=top style=\'width:450.7pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\'>  <p class=MsoNormal style=\'tab-stops:366.0pt\'><span style=\'font-size:9.0pt;  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;  mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:  Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\'>通过分布式hadoop集群处理每天从BSBank核心中获取的流水信息、HR系统绩效信息、运管平台的差错、核实、预警等数据，以计划任务调度的方式，每天通过MR过滤后产生相应的基础数据，保存在DB2中。<br />Java开发，配置计划任务调度器<br />1. 凌晨MDS跑批数据结束后，通知MR进行数据过滤<br />2. 定时调度使用Hive进行数据的多维分析<br />3. 将Hive分析结果导入到DB2中<br />4. 通过Kettle模版，产生相应的各个报表基础数据<br />5. 产生抽数日志记录，发生错误会推送相应错误代码到设置的运维人员邮箱</span>  <span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:9.0pt\'><o:p></o:p></span></p>  </td> </tr></table>', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '2017-03-01 17:57:50');

